doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    title
      | MuMoAfruika | INFO CURRATING
    link( rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-PsH8R72JQ3SOdhVi3uxftmaW6Vc51MKb0q5P2rRUpPvrszuE4W1povHYgTpBfshb" crossorigin="anonymous")
    link(  rel="stylesheet",href='css/select/select2.min.css')
    link(  rel="stylesheet",href='css/emailinfocurrating.css')
    link( href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Anton', rel="stylesheet")
    meta(name='google-site-verification' content='V3cAR9sUqRJ6AFUOpLvM6ZQPcnRIdSLadAsQ70rt5DU')
  body.container-fluid
      header.row
        img(src='images/MuMoAfruika.png', alt='MuMoAfruika logo')
      #welcomedialog.row
        #head
          h1 WELCOME TO MuMoAfruika
        #section
          p
            | Thank you for visiting our page.
            br
            | Whilst we are still in development, we would like you to be able to sign up for our email blast to stay updated with our development progress.
            br
            | In addition to being able to sign up for our email blast, we will be able to give you exclusive and first access to our platform when its ready.
          button#close CONTINUE
      section.maincontent.row
        .col-sm-4
          h1 SELECT A USER TYPE
        .col-sm-8
          p
            | User driven streaming is only one of the many features that will make you fall in love with us.
            br
            | To get to know our different user types and to also subscribe to our email blast, please use the drop down menu to select one:
          #userselection(class='row')
            #artist(class='col-sm')
              | ARTISTS & CONTENT CREATORS
            #producer(class='col-sm')
              | PRODUCERS, STUDIOS & COMPANIES
            #fan(class='col-sm')
              | CONTENT FANS
        #unsubscribe(style='display:none')
      section.usertypes.row
        .col-sm-4
        .col-sm-8(id='getemail')
      section.cd-horizontal-timeline.container-fluid(style='display:none')
        table.table.table-responsive-md
          thead
            tr
              th
                a INFORMATION GATHERING & ANALYSIS
                button.done DONE
              th.selected
                a(href='#0') DESIGN
                button.progress IN PROGRESS
              th.inactive
                a UI & UX DEVELOPMENT
              th.inactive
                a FUNCTIONAL DEVELOPMENT
              th.inactive
                a BETA FUNCTION TEST-1
          tbody
            tr
              td(colspan='5')
                | In this phase we are focusing on the graphical design part of our development process. This is chosing color palettes, the types of buttons, and every other nitty gritty visual aspect that will end up on our platform. The main inspiration behind our design choices will be to showcase Africa's exuberance. We are almost done with our design and about to move on to our next phase.
      footer.row
        .col-sm-12
          a.col-sm  DEVELOPMENT PROGRESS
          a.col-sm  ABOUT MuMoAfruika
        .col-sm-12
          a.col-sm(href='http://www.facebook.com/mumoafruika')
            img(src='images/fb.png', alt='facebook logo link')
          a.col-sm(href='https://www.instagram.com/mumoafruika')
            img(src='images/ig.png', alt='instagram logo link')
      script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js', integrity='sha256-FgpCb/KJQlLNfOu91ta32o/NMZxltwRo8QtmkMRdAu8=', crossorigin='anonymous')
      script(src='/js/sticky/jquery.sticky.js')
      script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.3/umd/popper.min.js', integrity='sha384-vFJXuSJphROIrBnz7yo7oB41mKfc8JzQZiCq4NCceLEaO4IHwicKwpJf9c9IpFgh', crossorigin='anonymous')
      script(src='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/js/bootstrap.min.js', integrity='sha384-alpBpkh1PFOepccYVYDB4do5UnbKysX5WZXm3XxPqe5iKTfUKjNkCk9SaVuEZflJ', crossorigin='anonymous')
      script(src='js/select/js/select2.full.min.js', defer='')
      script(src='js/emailinfocurrating.js', defer='')
